- Change module name from PyLDAP to avoid confusion with python-ldap.
- Rearrange source code into folders.
- Upload to PyPI.
- Complete Unicode support on Windows (while keeping compatibility with Linux).
- Improve sort control.
- Feature: Add LDIF reader and writer function.
- Feature: Add password modify extended operation.
- Feature: Possibility to change LDAPEntry and LDAPValueList to other dict and list based objects.
- Feature: SASL EXTERNAL authentication.
- Feature: Client-side validation for entries (with defined schemas).
